    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "目前业务上是一份CV对应一个Screening Result，一对一关系。不过为了扩展性，可以考虑一对多。我们先按一对一实现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CV",
        "SCREENING_RESULT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把主要实体和关系画出来了。Recruiter包含recruiterId、username、password和companyName。Job Post那边需要recruiterId作为外键。",
      "elements_involved": [
